description:
This is a 15 minute workout called '15 Minute Beginner Indoor Cycling Session' from the channel GCN Training.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Foundation Builder vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.

Original workout description: Welcome to a gentle, short workout here on GCN Training. This week's session is aimed at beginner cyclists looking to start training indoors, or it could be a good one for a rider looking to ease back into training after an injury or long lay off.

The Session:
Warm up: 
1 Min very easy pedalling
- 1 Min slight increase in intensity
1 Min further increase intensity to comfortably hard

Main set
1 Min Easy (1/10)
- 2 Min Comfortably hard (5/10)
1 Min Easy (1/10)
- 1 Min comfortably hard (5/10)
2 Increase effort (6/10) 
- 30s Easy (1/10)
30s Sprint (9/10)
- 2 Mins Recovery (1/10)
1 Min Comfortably hard (5/10)

- 1 Min Very easy cool down (1/10)
